do-install:
	${INSTALL_SCRIPT} ${FILESDIR}/autoconf ${STAGEDIR}${PREFIX}/bin/
.for l in autoheader autom4te autoreconf autoscan autoupdate ifnames
	${LN} -s autoconf ${STAGEDIR}${PREFIX}/bin/${l}
.endfor

[FILE:282:descriptions/desc.single]
This port installs a wrapper script for each tool included with autoconf.
The script will run the version of autoconf specified in the environment
variable DEFAULT_AUTOCONF.  If DEFAULT_AUTOCONF is empty or unset it will
run the most recent version of autoconf currently installed.


